[Name] ITSTool
[Summary] Internationalization Tag Set tool
[Description] Itstool extracts messages from XML files and outputs PO template
files, then merges translations from MO files to create translated XML files.
It determines what to translate and how to chunk it into messages using the
W3C Internationalization Tag Set (ITS). 
